{
  "stem": "23742.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came home on leave in September of that year, my first time in two years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And while I was home, it was V-E Day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember that quite clearly, because I think my son was conceived that night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We had extra leave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was great.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The war was over, both in Europe and in-- in the Far East.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I still had to return to my unit, even though the war had finished.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was ultimately-- I went back to Brussels to work on routine communications, routine duties.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was ultimately demobilized on the 1st of January 1946, after five and a half years in the army.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I returned to civilian life, which is extremely difficult.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean settling down after that, it was-- I was very-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was difficult to get along with.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "By that time, my wife and I had a home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had a flat in a house in South London.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it took quite a long time for me to settle down to what was a normal civilian life.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't have nightmares.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we talked a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of people and Jewish organizations, and even non-Jewish organizations, once-- once troops began to come back who had been involved in Germany, they wanted to hear first-hand information as to what really went on.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Bergen-Belsen was the only concentration camp in the British sector, which was-- Bergen-Belsen was near Hanover in North Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Most of the other concentration camps were either in-- mostly, were in the Russian or the American sectors, like Buchenwald and Auschwitz and all those other places.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But Bergen-Belsen was the only camp in the British sector.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
